'''''Hayat''''' ({{lang-fa|حیات}}) is an [[Iran]]ian newspaper in [[Fars Province]]. The [[concessionaire]] of this magazine was ''Mohammad Hosein Shari'at'' and it was published in [[Shiraz]] since 1910.<ref>Rumi,Siroos; List of printed matters of Fars;2006;[[Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance (Iran)]]</ref>

